title: Billy Joel - Greatest Hits I & II [Audiophile][FLAC]
description:
This version of Billy Joel's Greatest Hits Volume I & II has been remastered using audiophile releases of his individual albums wherever possible for the best sound quality. This will be the best sounding edition of this double album you will hear until MoFi releases their version. Eventually...
